    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297960/extras/12cd3ceee69dd18b9611cd9317015b6f.poster.avif?t=1737993492\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297960/extras/12cd3ceee69dd18b9611cd9317015b6f.webm?t=1737993492\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297960/extras/12cd3ceee69dd18b9611cd9317015b6f.mp4?t=1737993492\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>跟隨 <strong>Samuel </strong>, <strong>Sarah</strong>, 和 <strong>Clunky</strong>，在 <i>Relic Odyssey: Ruins of Xantao</i> 中進行一場危險的旅程。當你面對令人厭惡的野獸、無情的走私者以及神秘的 &quot;Collector&quot; ── 一個不擇手段要獲取 Xantao 遺址內隱藏的力量的瘋子時，請做好準備。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >冒險與戰鬥</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297960/extras/caceb4635ab570432ce8d881f4f7e59e.poster.avif?t=1737993492\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297960/extras/caceb4635ab570432ce8d881f4f7e59e.webm?t=1737993492\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297960/extras/caceb4635ab570432ce8d881f4f7e59e.mp4?t=1737993492\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>使用各種武器和小工具來 <strong>擊退</strong> 敵人。在你穿越研究中心、巢穴和遺址的過程中體驗不同類型的敵人和戰鬥風格！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索與發現</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297960/extras/800709941b5c20ae20fdeceb48b16726.poster.avif?t=1737993492\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297960/extras/800709941b5c20ae20fdeceb48b16726.webm?t=1737993492\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297960/extras/800709941b5c20ae20fdeceb48b16726.mp4?t=1737993492\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>使用你的 <strong>AVARITE POWERED GLOVES</strong> 掃描敵人和資源！通過在巢穴和遺址中推拉敵人來增加樂趣。使用同一能力來操縱你的環境！升級你的手套以解鎖特殊能力，如自動挖掘稀有資源、時間操縱、火焰、酸液和使敵人遭受電擊！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297960/extras/32c549afbc5e981b3780b61a3c27dc11.poster.avif?t=1737993492\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297960/extras/32c549afbc5e981b3780b61a3c27dc11.webm?t=1737993492\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297960/extras/32c549afbc5e981b3780b61a3c27dc11.mp4?t=1737993492\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>深入挖掘 Valtar 行星的神秘深處，尋找失落已久的 Xantao 城市。憑藉我們的 <strong>PROCEDURALLY GENERATED LEVELS</strong>，每次下降都是一個新挑戰，呈現新的環境、敵人和寶藏。從充滿晶體的洞穴到古老的地下遺址，穿越不可預測的地形。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297960/extras/95e1dfdf19d86ca78ac483b5609fced6.poster.avif?t=1737993492\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297960/extras/95e1dfdf19d86ca78ac483b5609fced6.webm?t=1737993492\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297960/extras/95e1dfdf19d86ca78ac483b5609fced6.mp4?t=1737993492\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>收集資源來進行 <strong>製作</strong> 新武器和升級！在巢穴和遺址中收集稀有資源，然後用它們製作技術，如移動醫療站和鑽探設備的升級。升級你的 <strong>DRILLING RIG</strong> 以增強其挖掘能力，挖掘更深，探索 Valtar 不斷變化的景觀。",
    "supported_languages": "英语<strong>*</strong>, 法语, 意大利语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 阿拉伯语, 保加利亚语, 捷克语, 丹麦语, 荷兰语, 芬兰语, 希腊语, 匈牙利语, 印度尼西亚语, 日语, 韩语, 挪威语, 波兰语, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 葡萄牙语 - 葡萄牙, 罗马尼亚语, 俄语, 简体中文, 西班牙语 - 拉丁美洲, 瑞典语, 泰语, 繁体中文, 土耳其语, 乌克兰语, 越南语<br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
